### Page 2

PROPRIETARY AND CONFIDENTIAL Inventory
© Cybersoft SchoolCafé www.schoolcafe.com Page 2 of 2

Click the + icon to withdraw additional Pack Sizes.
Click the Comments icon to add comments.
Click the Trash Can icon to delete the Item.

13. Click the NEXT button

In the Confirm section
14. Click the CONFIRM button
A success message displays.

WITHDRAWAL DETAILS OPTIONS
The Withdrawal Details page allows users to print the Withdrawal Ticket, view the Price Details Report, edit, and cancel
the Withdrawal.
The PRINT button allows users to view and
print the Withdrawal Ticket.
The PRICE button allows users to view and
print the Price Details Report.

The EDIT button allows users to edit the
Reason and the quantity withdrawn.
A comment is required for any changes.
The CANCEL button allows users to cancel the
Withdrawal.
A comment is required to cancel the
Withdrawal.

Click the BACK TO WITHDRAWAL LIST button
to return to the Withdrawals page.
